  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a zone that affects all ordinary characters, creatures without Chakra Reserves and creatures without any ranks in the Chakra Control skill. The zone does not move with you, and you can concentrate on it only while you remain within it. Subjects automatically ignore all sights and sounds from within the zone, as though they were completely unimportant and not worthy of attention. They will avoid entering the zone if possible, or will attempt to leave as soon as possible if they are forced inside. Each round they spend inside the zone, they can retry their save against the technique.<br><br>Dangerous effects (such as attacks) or extremely obvious events (like an explosion) coming from within the zone are not ignored, and allow subjects to make another Will save to disbelieve.<br><br>Cannot be dispelled.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first, third and fifth steps increase the radius of the zone by 10 ft.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
